<HEADLINE>
<P>
GIRLS' BASKETBALL ROUNDUP; SHINE, EL MODENA DEFENSE LEAD 51-36 UPSET OF 
10TH-RANKED VILLA PARK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Jamie Shine had 19 points and 14 rebounds to help El Modena to a 51-36 upset 
of Villa Park, the 10th-ranked team in Orange County, in a Century League 
girls' basketball game Thursday at El Modena. 
</P>
<P>
 Norah Mariner added 14 points and nine rebounds for El Modena (8-9, 4-2). 
</P>
<P>
 Villa Park is (17-3, 5-1). El Modena held Maureen Skehan, Villa Park's leading 
scorer at 16.3 points a game, to six points before she fouled out. 
</P>
