 Pacific Enterprises -- James R. Ukropina was president of Pacific Enterprises 
from 1986 through 1989, when he became chairman and chief executive. Paul A. 
Miller was chief executive from 1968 through 1989. An article in Thursday's 
editions incorrectly identified Ukropina as chief executive in 1986. 
